most trend in engineering, why, argument, model answer on the question

#1Модель ответа на вопрос
1. Topic - сказать то о чем будешь говорить
2. main idea - суть
3. firstly - пояснение
4. secondly - аргументы
5. thirdly
6. overall in general - подытожить
-> 1.

1. The most trending in engineering is environmental friendliness materials (or ecology).
2. Environmental friendliness materials is products dont emit toxic substances and not so dangerous for peoples health.
3. This materials is cheaper than analogs.
4. Materials doesnt exist toxic compounds and radioactive particles.
5. After end of cycle building materials can be recycled.
6. In general environmental friendliness materials better for the whole planet.


